@startuml
title 2PC Checkout - Combined View
hide footbox

participant Client
participant "Order service" as Order
participant Coordinator
participant "Stock service" as Stock
participant "Payment service" as Payment
participant "Recovery worker" as Recovery

legend right
|<#2E8B57>| normal progress |
|<#B22222>| failure branch |
|<#D97706>| recovery or undo |
endlegend

note over Client,Recovery #FFF8DC
Recovery may finish the transaction after the original
client request has already timed out.
end note

Client -[#2E8B57]> Order : Ask to check out the order.

alt The order does not exist
  Order -[#B22222]> Client : Reject the request.
  note over Client,Order #FDEDEC
  End: request rejected.
  end note

else Another checkout already holds the guard
  Order -[#B22222]> Client : Reject the request because checkout is already in progress.
  note over Client,Order #FDEDEC
  End: request rejected.
  end note

else The order is already paid
  Order -[#2E8B57]> Client : Return success immediately.
  note over Client,Order #E8F8F5
  End: already paid success.
  end note

else The order is valid and no other checkout is running
  Order -[#2E8B57]> Order : Validate the order and acquire the checkout guard.
  Order -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : Start the coordinator transaction.

  group PREPARE stage
    par Stock PREPARE branch
      Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Stock : Try to reserve the items for PREPARE.
    else Payment PREPARE branch
      Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Payment : Try to reserve the money for PREPARE.
    end

    alt Both PREPARE replies say ok
      Stock -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : PREPARE ok.
      Payment -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : PREPARE ok.
      Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : Record COMMIT and write the commit fence.

      group COMMIT stage
        par Stock COMMIT branch
          Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Stock : Finish COMMIT for the reservation.
        else Payment COMMIT branch
          Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Payment : Finish COMMIT for the money hold.
        end

        alt Both COMMIT confirmations arrive
          Stock -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
          Payment -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
          Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Order : Mark the order as paid.

          alt The order write succeeds
            Order -[#2E8B57]> Order : Clear the checkout guard.
            Order -[#2E8B57]> Client : Return success.
            note over Client,Order #E8F8F5
            End: success.
            end note

          else The order write fails
            Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : The transaction needs recovery after participants committed.
            note over Coordinator,Recovery #FDEDEC
            This branch covers:
            - order database write failed after both participants committed
            - a retry sees the transaction in COMMITTING
              but the order is still not paid
            end note

            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Inspect the durable markers and finish COMMIT.
            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Mark the order as paid if it is not paid yet.
            Order -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard.
            note over Order,Recovery #E8F8F5
            End: success after recovery.
            end note
          end

        else A COMMIT confirmation is missing,\na COMMIT publish fails,\na participant returns an error,\na wrong-phase reply is ignored,\nor the coordinator stops after COMMIT was chosen
          Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : The transaction needs recovery after COMMIT was chosen.
          note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
          This branch covers:
          - stock COMMIT confirmation lost
          - payment COMMIT confirmation lost
          - COMMIT publish failure
          - participant error during COMMIT
          - stale PREPARE reply ignored while waiting for COMMIT
          - coordinator crash after the COMMIT decision
            or the commit fence already existed
          end note

          Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Inspect the durable markers and finish COMMIT.

          par Finish stock COMMIT
            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the reservation.
            Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
          else Finish payment COMMIT
            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the money hold.
            Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
          end

          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Mark the order as paid if it is not paid yet.
          Order -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard.
          note over Order,Recovery #E8F8F5
          End: success after recovery.
          end note
        end
      end

    else PREPARE does not finish cleanly,\nor the coordinator stops before COMMIT is safely decided
      Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : Record ABORT and start RELEASE now.
      note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
      This branch covers:
      - stock reject
      - payment reject
      - timeout or lost reply
      - PREPARE publish failure
      - coordinator crash before the COMMIT decision
        and commit fence were durable
      end note

      group Presumed abort work
        par Undo stock PREPARE
          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : RELEASE the reservation if one exists.
        else Undo payment PREPARE
          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : RELEASE the money hold if one exists.
        end

        alt Both RELEASE confirmations arrive
          Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
          Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
          note over Order,Recovery #FCF3CF
          End: checkout aborted.
          end note

        else A RELEASE confirmation is missing,\na RELEASE publish fails,\na participant returns an error,\na wrong-phase reply is ignored,\nor the coordinator stops during abort
          Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : The transaction now needs recovery.
          note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
          This branch covers:
          - stock RELEASE confirmation lost
          - payment RELEASE confirmation lost
          - RELEASE publish failure
          - participant error during RELEASE
          - stale PREPARE reply ignored while waiting for RELEASE
          - coordinator crash during presumed abort
          end note

          Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Inspect the transaction state and choose the safe next step.

          alt A COMMIT decision, a commit fence,\nor a paid order already exists
            note over Recovery,Coordinator #FFF4E5
            Recovery must move forward because the transaction
            is already committed enough that presumed abort
            is no longer safe.
            end note

            par Finish stock COMMIT
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the reservation.
              Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            else Finish payment COMMIT
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the money hold.
              Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            end

            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Mark the order as paid if it is not paid yet.
            Order -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard.
            note over Order,Recovery #E8F8F5
            End: success after recovery.
            end note

          else No durable marker says COMMIT won
            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Continue RELEASE work.

            par Continue stock abort
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : RELEASE the reservation if one exists.
              Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
            else Continue payment abort
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : RELEASE the money hold if one exists.
              Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
            end

            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
            note over Order,Recovery #FCF3CF
            End: checkout aborted after recovery.
            end note
          end
        end
      end
    end
  end
end
@enduml
